arStrings.szText: "This hardly seems like a place for children."
They have nowhere else to go. Their families fled Jirandai to escape the horrors of the north, but the cannibals found them anyway.
Saddened. Clearly pities the victims of the cannibals.
Other travelers are in peril while those accursed flesh-eaters roam the roads. Should you thin their numbers, I can offer a portion of our tithes.
